The "Permanent" Way: NodePort

If you want to access the UI using the IP address of your RHEL nodes (e.g., http://192.168.x.x:32000), you need to change the Service type.

Step A: Patch the services to NodePort

# Change Grafana to NodePort
kubectl patch svc prom-demo-grafana -n monitoring -p '{"spec": {"type": "NodePort"}}'

# Change Prometheus to NodePort
kubectl patch svc prom-demo-kube-prometheus-prometheus -n monitoring -p '{"spec": {"type": "NodePort"}}'

